<div id="review_1953747707" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1953747707" />
    <a title="Starjustin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/61242604-starjustin"><img alt="Starjustin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1484505801p2/61242604.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1953747707?book_show_action=true">Mar 27, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Starjustin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Starjustin" href="/user/show/61242604-starjustin">Starjustin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback " href="/book/show/5470.1984">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1953747707" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9790876903161912774">What can I possibly say about this amazing novel, 1984 by George Orwell, that hasn&apos;t been already said by many who have read the book for over half a century. When it is said that the book is &apos;haunting&apos;, &apos;nightmarish&apos;, and &apos;startling&apos; any reader would have to agree! This well known novel grips the reader from the beginning and does not even let go of the grip at the finished reading. A classic you won&apos;t want to miss if you haven&apos;t taken the time to read it yet. <br/>I actually listened to this novel </span>
  <span id="freeText9790876903161912774" style="display:none">What can I possibly say about this amazing novel, 1984 by George Orwell, that hasn't been already said by many who have read the book for over half a century. When it is said that the book is 'haunting', 'nightmarish', and 'startling' any reader would have to agree! This well known novel grips the reader from the beginning and does not even let go of the grip at the finished reading. A classic you won't want to miss if you haven't taken the time to read it yet. <br />I actually listened to this novel on audio and Simon Prebble was the 'perfect' narrator.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9790876903161912774" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

